  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the quiet village of Pinzolo and surrounded by the Brenta dolomites, the Hotel Canada has a great location close to the lifts.</p>
<h2>Close to Pinzolo lifts</h2>
<p>Located just 20 minutes outside of <a data-udi="umb://document/ea59b48ae29b417b81f9c9850d58d038" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ea59b48ae29b417b81f9c9850d58d038}" title="Madonna Di Campiglio">Madonna di Campiglio</a>, Pinzolo offers a more laid-back, local atmosphere. Rest assured that you have access to the same expansive ski area as Madonna di Campiglio by taking the gondola from the village into the mountains.</p>
<p>Hotel Canada has an excellent location in Pinzolo, just 300 metres from the Prà Rodont lift. From here you have amazing linked access to the Madonna di Campiglio ski area with 155 kms of pistes, ideal for beginners and intermediates.</p>
<h2>Swimming pool</h2>
<p>The hotel has a great wellness facilities including a heated indoor swimming pool with views of the hotel's gardens. There is an adults-only spa area featuring outdoor hot tub, Turkish bath, Finnish sauna, Kneipp path and tropical shower.</p>
<h2>Family friendly</h2>
<p>This family-friendly hotel is lovingly run by the Maffei sisters and they provide a warm welcome and personal service to all guests. The hotel runs an evening mini-club for children aged 3 and up from 4pm-7pm.</p>]]></description>
